re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"其實真係睇誠哥做乜就知佢咩睇法<br />\n<br />\n做生意最緊要係自由穩定嘅營商環境<br />\n<br />\n環境係由人話事<br />\n<br />\n定<br />\n<br />\n環境由文字（法律） 話事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傻嘅都識揀"},{"pid":"460bb88bc3d6076a70935be95b13e6f5317a0332","tid":536953,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:26:25.000Z","msg":"一壇連誠哥都唔做既生意<br />\n前景係點大家心中有數"},{"pid":"df872e1e2e7300fa4275998ea1e3218bffb1e517","tid":536953,"uid":51294,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:28:59.000Z","msg":"佢重慶塊地廿幾億買，二百幾億放。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f584a8728c86aa4d3c61d904855c1811a93d8c37","tid":536953,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fad9d8ec82953ff6c8743c5d5cfe14e2f0733f9","tid":536953,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢重慶塊地廿幾億買，二百幾億放。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曬左太陽十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係李嘉誠個名都值唔少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢出名好眼光，就算真係爛地都會有人接手"},{"pid":"fbb471476c3a9861ea87c2bcaca2199e32785cd0","tid":536953,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"似係Victor唔想/唔識同共產黨打交道"},{"pid":"fb6e7aa5204f6c2b59016e424012f91b6594a0fa","tid":536953,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"留意一點：習近平既 「打貪」行動係無一個停止時間<br />\n而佢既「打貪」實際上係咩黎大家都知"},{"pid":"241bcef3ba43bc6a9406d65cee9e9aa39bba4b08","tid":536953,"uid":34666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb6e7aa5204f6